No. 87,

Misc.

The Romanian Orthodox Missionary Episcopate of America, through His Grace Bishop Andrei Moldovan, v. Trutza et al. John R. Vintilla for petitioner. Percy H. Russell for respondents.

The motion to use record in No. 422, October Term, 1953, is granted. Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari denied.
